Subject: [PATCH 34/44] Terminate browser on host disconnect

---
 chrome/browser/cbf/cbf_browser_service.cc     | 26 ++++++++++++
 chrome/browser/cbf/cbf_browser_service.h      |  7 ++++
 .../cbf/cbf_browser_service_unittest.cc       | 40 +++++++++++++++++++
 chrome/browser/cbf/cbf_service.cc             |  3 +-
